{ White has a slight, but decent edge.   The control over the squares c5 and d5 will be useful and Nb3, Ne3 is a possible example for the placement of the Knights. The Knight can also control the c5-square from e4.   In general if White manages to achieve d5, White will have an excellent position, which was how the game Kryvoruchko - Aditya, 2019 went. }
