{ White can actually go e4 right away as Black cannot take on e4 due to the hanging d6-pawn.   However, to get in e5, White would require support with Re1 in any case. }
13... b5 14. axb5 axb5 15. Ra7 { White indirectly threatens e5. } 15... b4 16.
Na4
